OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784047674
OL,3,CDog gets Stranraer lifeboat VIP
OL,4,Ctreatment during medical emergency
OL,6,FStranraer RNLI's volunteer lifeboat
OL,7,Fcrew has wished a man who suffered a
OL,8,Fmedical emergency on Saturday July
OL,9,F11th a speedy recovery, after
OL,10,Freuniting him with his dog.
OL,12,FThe vessel became grounded south of
OL,13,FLoch Ryan, so the crew first launched
OL,14,Fat approximately 10.30am, after
OL,15,Freports it had got into difficulty.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
