PN,32705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784047674
OL,3,CDog gets Stranraer lifeboat VIP
OL,4,Ctreatment during medical emergency
OL,6,FOur volunteer crew responded to a
OL,7,Fgrounded vessel in the morning and
OL,8,Flater returned to find the situation
OL,9,Fhad developed into a medical emergency.
OL,11,FThanks to the close cooperation
OL,12,Fbetween HM Coastguard, Stranraer
OL,13,FCoastguard Rescue Team, the Scottish
OL,14,FAmbulance Service and our volunteer
OL,15,Fcrew, the casualty received prompt
OL,16,Fmedical attention and the vessel was
OL,17,Fsafely recovered. We wish the
OL,18,Fgentleman involved a speedy recovery."
OL,26,@zD@fO]
